title: College football's Firefly Funhouse
description:
When you have to confront your evil self in a nightmare zone, that's a spring game.
Introducing MORON OPERA, America's finest storytelling mode
When a rasslin match convinces you the evil clown is the good guy
Florida faces its demons in the funhouse
NC State faces its horrifying LACK OF A FACE!
And a swamplord from USC's past returns with vengeance
Also, football coaches, please just read the card and stop ad-libbing about the pandemic, thanks
